        "text": ".—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "HANGING.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(22) And he be put to death.—Better, and he hath been put to death. Hanging followed death in Israel (Joshua 10:26-27).",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(22) ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "And he be put to death.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Better, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "and he hath been put to death. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Hanging ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "followed ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "death in Israel (",
            "children": []
